title: Real Money
overview: Real Money following the daily lives of multi-platinum rock legend Eddie Money and his family. The series will include candid moments with Money as he deals with the struggles and joys of life at home with his wife, eight pets, and five wild and talented children. The series is as honest and open as it is heartfelt and hilarious, capturing every moment of the family's unique dynamic as they live, laugh, bicker, and rock under one roof.
